vote.title: Authorization of (1) an ordinance (a) repealing Ordinance No. 31521; (b) providing a saving clause; and (c) providing an effective date (Attachment A); and (2) a temporary ordinance (a) providing for a notice of proposed eviction by residential landlords before a notice to vacate a residential tenancy; (b) creating an offense; (c) providing a penalty not to exceed $500.00; (d) providing a savings clause; (e) providing a severability clause; and (f) providing an effective date (Attachment B) - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
